text: Yulin Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Xinfu District, Fushun, Liaoning, China. , it has 3 residential communities and 2 villages under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Liaoning == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Liaoning Category:Fushun
